translation.Name: Irish Note - Plane Crash
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: MAYDAY MAYDAY MAYDAY. Waterford Airport, this is Flight-219. I don’t know what the hell is going on but the passengers are killing each other back here. My flight attendant said it was a bloodbath before she herself was pulled into it. I tried to help her, I did, but one of those freaks bit me, and I had to retreat to the cockpit and lock the door. I’m requesting an immediate police and medical response as I intend to land at your airport.
